title: Dil Ne Phir Yaad Kiya
subTitle: Ashok, a salesman, is in love with Ashoo and wants to marry her. However, things take a turn when his brother kidnaps Ashoo.

title: Chalti Ka Naam Gaadi
subTitle: Brijmohan, a mechanic, swears off women after a bad experience. However, when a headstrong woman arrives at his garage, he is forced to reconsider his opinion.

title: Pataal Bhairavi
subTitle: Ramu, a poor man, falls for a princess, but her father forbids the relation due to Ramu's poverty. Later, things take a turn for the worse when Ramu becomes rich, but it endangers his paramour.

title: Classic Legends
subTitle: Host Javed Akhtar presents the lives and careers of the greatest personalities of the golden era of Bollywood, as a tribute to their work.

title: Bandini
subTitle: Devendra, a doctor working at a women's prison, falls for Kalyani, a convicted prisoner. However, things become complicated as the tale behind her crimes unfolds.

title: Neela Aakash
subTitle: Neela and Akash fall in love with each other after a comedy of errors. But her drunkard father disapproves of their union as she is the sole breadwinner of their family.

title: Jheel Ke Us Paar
subTitle: Sameer falls in love with Neelu, a girl with visual impairment, and plans to restore her sight. However, his mother disapproves of their union and hatches a plot to break them apart.

title: Insaaf Ki Pukar
subTitle: When a dishonest officer destroys their lives, two men unite to fight corruption, facing danger as they strive to restore honour and peace.

title: Jeevan Mrityu
subTitle: Upon his release from exile, Ashok's life turns upside down when he learns about his mother's death and the truth behind his false accusation.

title: Qayamat
subTitle: Two close friends turn enemies when one becomes a criminal and the other, an IPS officer. Wronged by his friend, the criminal swears to take revenge once he returns from prison.

title: Somnath Jyotirlinga
subTitle: A dramatised chronicle depicting the historical circumstances of the inception and evolution of Somnath Temple, one of the twelve jyotirlinga shrines of Lord Shiva.

title: Bhuvan Shome

title: Chandan Ka Palna
subTitle: Ajit's perfect marriage to Shobha turns upside down after she starts behaving strangely with him and his mother, leading to a disturbed life.

title: Samadhi
subTitle: Lakhan Singh gives up his life of crime when he falls in love and marries Champa. However, things take a turn when she falls sick and he is forced to become a criminal again.

title: Mera Gaon Mera Desh

title: Batwara
subTitle: Amidst the fall of princely states in post-independence India, the friendship between aristocrat Vikram and a peasant is tested. Vikram turns vengeful after his brother is killed in a peasant colony.

title: Razia Sultan
subTitle: Razia Sultan, the first female ruler of the Delhi Sultanate, lands in trouble and loses her kingdom when she falls in love with Jamal-ud-Din Yakut, an Abyssinian slave.

title: Dost
subTitle: Maanav befriends Gopichand, a reformed thief, and helps him secure a job to turn his life around. However, Maanav suddenly disappears and returns just in time to support Gopichand during a crisis.
